sudo yum update

sudo amazon-linux-extras install nginx1

sudo systemctl start nginx
sudo systemctl restart nginx

Check by typing public ip in web browser
you will see the nginx page

now move to ngnix folder by typing

cd /usr/share/ngnix/html

run ls and remove the .html file

ls
sudo rm index.html

create new file or get the github link repo of this folder
copy index.html and a.png

to create new index.html file type

sudo vi index.html
and run
sudo systemctl restart ngninx

